WEBVTT

00:00.951 --> 00:02.885
Tomorrow's Big Trash Day,

00:02.887 --> 00:05.020
the garbage men's
favorite day of the year.

00:05.022 --> 00:08.490
But this is Big Trash Eve... my time,

00:08.492 --> 00:10.425
when the streets are lined with gold!

00:10.427 --> 00:12.160
Isn't all this stuff broken?

00:12.162 --> 00:15.164
What's broken about a mirrored
headboard with a crack in it?

00:15.166 --> 00:16.565
A toilet with no seat?

00:16.567 --> 00:18.033
Most of a hose?

00:18.035 --> 00:20.569
Ooh! What's that?

00:20.571 --> 00:23.172
This might be the last big TV.

00:23.174 --> 00:24.439
It's so deep.

00:24.441 --> 00:27.176
I have to get this home it's so deep.

00:29.179 --> 00:30.645
So heavy.

00:30.647 --> 00:32.781
So splintery.

00:32.783 --> 00:35.518
All the weight is distributed so oddly.

00:35.520 --> 00:36.919
This, I like.

00:36.921 --> 00:39.454
This speaks to me.

00:39.456 --> 00:41.524
Mm. Nice, loud springs.

00:41.526 --> 00:44.059
Baby lambs on a soiled comforter.

00:44.061 --> 00:45.895
And hello!

00:47.998 --> 00:49.464
Dare I?

00:49.857 --> 00:51.133
Perfect fit!

00:51.135 --> 00:52.801
Stan, you can finally take me back

00:52.803 --> 00:55.270
