01:53.998 --> 01:55.864
Some dirty-ass mattress?

01:55.866 --> 01:57.399
Stop being outrageous. Look.

01:57.401 --> 02:00.535
There's a beautiful
Spanish word painted on it.

02:00.537 --> 02:02.671
- _
