02:39.910 --> 02:42.777
That thing can't stay in here.
It could fall on the baby.

02:42.779 --> 02:45.614
Maybe it <i>should</i> fall on the baby.

02:50.254 --> 02:54.123
I'll never understand
the weight distribution.

02:59.240 --> 03:00.695
Fake baby.

03:00.697 --> 03:03.298
This TV is what's real... real fun.

03:03.300 --> 03:05.634
What's this smushed
into the cable input?

03:05.636 --> 03:07.436
Hmm. Dog shit.

03:07.438 --> 03:08.671
I'll use the antenna.

03:10.507 --> 03:11.840
What a blast.

03:11.842 --> 03:13.476
It's a party down here.

03:15.646 --> 03:17.446
Hmm. No signal.

03:17.448 --> 03:19.715
Let's try the old splits.

03:19.745 --> 03:21.250
Nothing.

03:21.252 --> 03:22.918
Do a little scissor kick.

03:22.920 --> 03:24.052
Side saddle?

03:24.054 --> 03:26.521
Nope. Now the one
people don't like to see,

03:26.523 --> 03:27.990
but sometimes it works.

03:27.992 --> 03:31.260
Both of them together straight up!

03:31.262 --> 03:32.327
Hmm.

