The hour's late,
but the party is just getting started.

04:17.440 --> 04:18.841
I'm Alistair Covax,

04:18.843 --> 04:23.178
your host for a sophisticated
little soiree with jazz,

04:23.180 --> 04:26.581
stimulating conversation,
beautiful ladies,

04:26.583 --> 04:29.051
and more jazz.

04:29.053 --> 04:30.385
Hmm.

04:30.387 --> 04:31.720
Look. It's Charlie,

04:31.722 --> 04:34.657
sincerely one of the best white,
non-union jazz pianists

04:34.659 --> 04:36.859
in the entire city... top five.

04:36.861 --> 04:40.195
Charlie, play some
of those notes you know I like.

04:42.199 --> 04:44.199
What is this show?

04:45.336 --> 04:47.602
No results for Alistair Covax.

04:47.604 --> 04:49.472
"Nighthawks' Hideaway."

04:49.474 --> 04:52.607
Nothing. Why is there
no record of this show?

04:52.609 --> 04:54.076
I need answers.

04:54.078 --> 04:55.578
TV answers.

04:55.579 --> 04:56.679
_

04:59.350 --> 05:02.617
The star's of "Hawaii Five-O"
are in a prank war!

05:02.619 --> 05:05.488
You think "Wheel of Fortune"
is on at 8:00?

05:05.490 --> 05:07.089
You're fired!

05:07.091 --> 05:09.492
- What, what, what?!
- I recently came into possession

05:09.494 --> 05:12.160
of a deep TV...
no need to congratulate me...

05:12.162 --> 05:16.031
and I saw a 1960s show called
"Nighthawks' Hideaway."

05:16.033 --> 05:17.632
There's no such show.

05:17.634 --> 05:19.568
There's never been such a show.

05:19.570 --> 05:22.304
But every few months, some lonely nutjob

05:22.306 --> 05:24.239
comes in asking about it.

05:24.241 --> 05:26.909
Oh, trust me. I am not a nutjob.

05:26.911 --> 05:28.577
Good. Good.

05:28.579 --> 05:31.046
Word is these nutjobs get together

05:31.048 --> 05:33.648
at the Ukrainian Cultural Center

05:33.650 --> 05:36.585
to talk about this show
that doesn't exist.

05:36.587 --> 05:38.053
Cultural Center, huh?

05:38.055 --> 05:39.855
I mean, I saw the show with my own eyes,

05:39.857 --> 05:42.324
but nutjobs like that make me sick.

05:42.326 --> 05:44.727
Me too, pal. You get it.

05:44.729 --> 05:46.729
Someone should round these nutjobs up,

05:46.731 --> 05:49.598
