and just drop it in the sea.

05:49.600 --> 05:52.334
Well, I don't know about that.

05:52.336 --> 05:55.044
- _
- _

05:55.139 --> 05:57.573
Hopefully these people
can give me some answers.

05:59.410 --> 06:01.009
Hi, Stan!

06:01.011 --> 06:02.945
Sit. Sit, sit, sit, sit, sit.

06:02.947 --> 06:05.814
Uh...

06:05.816 --> 06:08.551
So, you've seen the show.

06:08.553 --> 06:10.685
Yeah. Strange there's no record of it.

06:10.687 --> 06:12.487
It gets stranger than that.

06:12.489 --> 06:13.956
There's only one episode,

06:13.958 --> 06:16.892
and it reruns over and over
and over on Channel 36.

06:16.894 --> 06:19.294
And get this. Come closer. Come closer.

06:19.296 --> 06:21.496
No, thank you.

06:21.498 --> 06:24.899
There's only one episode,
but it changes...

06:24.901 --> 06:28.170
Little things,
little differences in the show.

06:28.172 --> 06:29.572
I keep track of them.

06:29.574 --> 06:30.905
Where's everybody else?

06:30.907 --> 06:32.507
There used to be more people,

06:32.509 --> 06:34.843
but one by one, they stopped coming.

06:34.845 --> 06:37.112
It's so good to have you here, Stan.

06:37.114 --> 06:38.914
It's not just me anymore.

06:38.916 --> 06:41.183
It's <i>you</i> and me cracking the case

06:41.185 --> 06:42.918
of the "Nighthawks' Hideaway."

06:42.920 --> 06:45.921
We're the same now... two men obsessed.

06:45.923 --> 06:49.124
Ooh! It's like I'm looking in a mirror!

06:49.126 --> 06:50.493
No, thank you.

06:52.329 --> 06:55.798
Sometimes when the jazz is playing,
I like to do this.

06:57.001 --> 06:59.602
I move my chin just a little.

07:01.872 --> 07:04.206
This strange show.

07:04.208 --> 07:06.742
You stop bothering Stan!

07:06.786 --> 07:09.278
Is... Is that...

07:09.280 --> 07:11.546
It couldn't be.

07:11.548 --> 07:12.615
Tuttle?

07:12.617 --> 07:14.749
No. That's impossible.

07:14.751 --> 07:16.418
Wow! Great jazz!

07:16.420 --> 07:18.887
Shh. We're appreciating the jazz.

07:18.889 --> 07:21.657
