07:44.887 --> 07:47.483
But maybe...

07:47.485 --> 07:49.585
Every time.

07:55.559 --> 07:57.960
Ugh. What is that smell?

08:02.766 --> 08:05.567
They're both contributing.

08:05.569 --> 08:07.503
There's a beauty.

08:09.907 --> 08:12.308
"I must go in!"

08:15.913 --> 08:18.380
A shadow puppet theater of sorts.

08:18.382 --> 08:20.916
I wish I had time for
such childish games.

08:20.918 --> 08:22.685
Duck! Duck, duck!

08:25.323 --> 08:27.589
May I hold baby Roger?

08:27.591 --> 08:29.191
Make sure to support his head.

08:29.193 --> 08:31.059
Yeah, no shit.

08:33.131 --> 08:35.597
You guys are not gonna
believe where Tuttle is.

08:35.599 --> 08:38.133
Come downstairs.

08:38.135 --> 08:39.868
I don't know why it's not coming in now.

08:39.870 --> 08:42.538
I saw him. Tuttle was inside the TV!

08:42.539 --> 08:46.742
Stan, you're down here by
yourself watching static.

08:46.744 --> 08:49.411
I can watch static upstairs.

08:49.413 --> 08:50.946
Why don't you come upstairs, Dad?

08:50.948 --> 08:53.149
Yeah, aren't you lonely down here?

08:53.151 --> 08:55.584
Lonely?! I have a TV!

08:57.821 --> 08:58.954
So itchy.

08:58.956 --> 09:01.757
Probably those fleece
pajamas I've been wearing.

09:01.759 --> 09:04.827
Tonight, I sleep on this mattress naked.

09:04.829 --> 09:06.562
