10:24.708 --> 10:26.242
Sleep training is cruel.

10:26.244 --> 10:27.589
I want to pick him up!

10:27.645 --> 10:29.511
You're both wrong. We need to give...

10:29.513 --> 10:32.248
- We're not giving him weed!
- It's a micro-dose

10:32.250 --> 10:33.644
to help him sleep.

10:33.984 --> 10:36.852
We need to get in there!
He's afraid of the dark!

10:36.854 --> 10:39.255
Oh. Leaving so soon?

10:39.257 --> 10:40.989
Well, our party keeps going.

10:40.991 --> 10:44.526
So, if it gets lonely out
there in the wee, small hours,

10:44.528 --> 10:46.528
remember, nighthawks,

10:46.530 --> 10:49.265
you always have a friend
here at the Hideaway.

10:52.069 --> 10:53.736
There must be something I missed.

11:08.752 --> 11:10.085
Hmm.

11:10.087 --> 11:11.620
Cannonball!

11:15.493 --> 11:18.026
Welcome, nighthawk.

11:18.028 --> 11:20.096
We've been expecting you.

11:20.098 --> 11:21.897
I'm in the TV!

11:21.899 --> 11:24.032
I'm so relieved I'm not crazy!

11:24.034 --> 11:26.702
It was just a magic TV, that's all.

11:26.704 --> 11:29.771
Yes, please.

11:29.773 --> 11:32.508
Charlie, play some
of those notes you know I like.

11:32.510 --> 11:35.243
What the hell is that floating light?

11:35.245 --> 11:37.245
Tuttle!

11:37.247 --> 11:39.114
Stan?

11:39.116 --> 11:40.649
I remember you.

11:40.651 --> 11:42.250
Of course. You remember me.
I'm... I'm like

11:42.252 --> 11:46.054
- your all-time favorite person.
- Oh, it's the rerunning.

11:46.056 --> 11:47.389
We just keep rerunning.

11:47.391 --> 11:48.790
I remember less each time.

11:48.792 --> 11:50.859
I'm forgetting my life, Sam!

11:50.861 --> 11:52.728
Tuttle, relax. You don't like it here,

11:52.730 --> 11:54.596
- let's just go.
- We can't.

11:54.598 --> 11:56.598
We're trapped here forever.

11:56.600 --> 11:59.335
Ooh. Does forever include this weekend?

11:59.337 --> 12:01.403
'Cause the BET Awards are on.

12:01.405 --> 12:03.138
BET Awards?

12:03.140 --> 12:04.673
I remember those.

12:04.675 --> 12:06.475
Those are from the future.

12:06.477 --> 12:07.876
I need to get back to the future.

12:08.525 --> 12:10.278
"Back to the Future"!

12:10.280 --> 12:12.080
I love that movie!

12:12.082 --> 12:13.415
And Michael J. Fox!

12:13.417 --> 12:14.750
He was so great!

12:14.752 --> 12:18.220
Then... that thing happened to him.

12:18.222 --> 12:20.022
Oh, then the Towers.

12:20.024 --> 12:22.758
Then that pretty good
Denis Leary firemen show.

12:22.760 --> 12:25.627
